f Section at Tarsheed, contributing to conservation, energy efficiency, and national sustainability goals in line with Qatar National Vision 2030.</p><div class=\"mt-9 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)\"><a href=\"#about\" class=\"group inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 h-12 rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-white bg-maroon hover:bg-maroon-strong border border-gold-soft transition-colors shadow-[0_8px_30px_-12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)]\">View Profile<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5 flip-rtl\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 h-12 rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-fg border border-border-strong hover:bg-fg/5 transition-colors\">Contact</a></div><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-8 gap-y-3 text-xs tracking-wide text-fg-subtle\" style=\"opacity:0\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin text-gold\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg>Doha, Qatar</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-gold-soft\"></span>KAHRAMAA · Tarsheed</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-gold-soft\"></span>Aligned with Qatar National Vision 2030</span></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-md\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px) scale(0.98)\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -inset-3 rounded-[22px] border border-gold-faint\"></div><div class=\"relative aspect-[4/5] rounded-[18px] overflow-hidden glass-strong\"><img alt=\"Muhannad Alyafei — Head of Section, Tarsheed\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 32vw, (min-width: 640px) 60vw, 90vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fportrait.jpeg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-1/3 bg-gradient-to-t from-bg/70 to-transparent\"></div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" class=\"absolute text-gold/70 top-3 left-3\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M1 8 V1 H8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><circle cx=\"1\" cy=\"1\" r=\"0.8\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" class=\"absolute text-gold/70 top-3 right-3 rotate-90\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M1 8 V1 H8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><circle cx=\"1\" cy=\"1\" r=\"0.8\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" class=\"absolute text-gold/70 bottom-3 left-3 -rotate-90\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M1 8 V1 H8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><circle cx=\"1\" cy=\"1\" r=\"0.8\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" class=\"absolute text-gold/70 bottom-3 right-3 rotate-180\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M1 8 V1 H8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><circle cx=\"1\" cy=\"1\" r=\"0.8\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg></div><div class=\"mt-5 glass rounded-xl px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between\"><div><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.24em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">Currently</p><p class=\"text-sm text-fg mt-0.5\">Head of Section · Tarsheed</p></div><span class=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-sage shadow-[0_0_0_4px_rgba(123,168,151,0.15)]\"></span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"about\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 \"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">About</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">A Qatari professional committed to national service.</h2></div></header><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><div class=\"space-y-6 text-[17px] leading-[1.85] text-fg-muted text-pretty\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p>A Qatari citizen and public-service professional working within Tarsheed — KAHRAMAA&#x27;s National Program for Conservation and Energy Efficiency. His work centers on leadership, public awareness, and the responsible stewardship of Qatar&#x27;s natural resources.</p></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p>As Head of Section, he leads a multidisciplinary team focused on strategic communication, community engagement, and sustainability initiatives that align with Qatar National Vision 2030. His approach pairs operational discipline with a deep commitment to the country, its people, and its future.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"mt-10 hairline-gold h-px w-full\"></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-gold italic\">“<!-- -->Service to Qatar is the foundation of every effort — today and for generations to come.<!-- -->”</p></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"glass rounded-2xl p-2\"><dl class=\"grid grid-cols-2 divide-x divide-y divide-border overflow-hidden rounded-xl\"><div class=\"p-5 md:p-6\"><dt class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">Role</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-fg\">Head of Section</dd></div><div class=\"p-5 md:p-6\"><dt class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">Program</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-fg\">Tarsheed</dd></div><div class=\"p-5 md:p-6\"><dt class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">Authority</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-fg\">KAHRAMAA</dd></div><div class=\"p-5 md:p-6\"><dt class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">Based in</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-fg\">Doha, Qatar</dd></div></dl></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"mt-6 glass rounded-2xl p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-sage\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-fg-subtle\">National Alignment</span></div><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-fg-muted leading-relaxed\">Working in line with Qatar National Vision 2030&#x27;s environmental development pillar — supporting a balanced approach to growth and resource stewardship.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"leadership\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,var(--accent-maroon-soft),transparent_60%)]\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 \"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">Leadership</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">A role built on stewardship, awareness, and impact.</h2></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p class=\"mt-5 text-base md:text-lg text-fg-muted text-pretty max-w-2xl\">As Head of Section, his responsibilities span communication, community engagement, and the long-term sustainability priorities of the program.</p></div></header><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square\"><path d=\"M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->1</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">Strategic Communication</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Shaping clear, credible messaging that supports national conservation priorities across audiences and channels.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->2</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">Community Awareness</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Driving public engagement that turns awareness into everyday habits across households, schools, and institutions.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-leaf\"><path d=\"M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z\"></path><path d=\"M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->3</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">Sustainability Initiatives</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Supporting initiatives that advance responsible consumption and long-term environmental stewardship.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-compass\"><path d=\"m16.24 7.76-1.804 5.411a2 2 0 0 1-1.265 1.265L7.76 16.24l1.804-5.411a2 2 0 0 1 1.265-1.265z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->4</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">Team Leadership</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Leading a multidisciplinary section with clarity, accountability, and a culture of public service.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-droplets\"><path d=\"M7 16.3c2.2 0 4-1.83 4-4.05 0-1.16-.57-2.26-1.71-3.19S7.29 6.75 7 5.3c-.29 1.45-1.14 2.84-2.29 3.76S3 11.1 3 12.25c0 2.22 1.8 4.05 4 4.05z\"></path><path d=\"M12.56 6.6A10.97 10.97 0 0 0 14 3.02c.5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5s3 3.5 3 5.5a6.98 6.98 0 0 1-11.91 4.97\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->5</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">Energy &amp; Water Conservation</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Contributing to programs that protect Qatar&#x27;s vital energy and water resources for future generations.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article class=\"group relative h-full glass rounded-2xl p-7 transition-all hover:border-gold-soft hover:bg-fg/[0.04]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 w-11 rounded-lg bg-maroon-soft border border-maroon-soft text-gold\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flag\"><path d=\"M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z\"></path><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"4\" y1=\"22\" y2=\"15\"></line></svg></span><span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-fg-faint\">0<!-- -->6</span></div><h3 class=\"mt-6 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg tracking-tight\">National Development</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Aligning section priorities with Qatar National Vision 2030 and the country&#x27;s broader development goals.</p><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gold-soft to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></article></div></div></div></section><section id=\"mission\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 \"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">Mission</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">Aligned with Tarsheed, KAHRAMAA, and Vision 2030.</h2></div></header><div class=\"space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-[1.85] text-fg-muted text-pretty max-w-xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p>Tarsheed is connected to conservation and energy efficiency efforts in Qatar under KAHRAMAA — the Qatar General Electricity &amp; Water Corporation. The program promotes responsible use of energy and water across the country, supporting national goals around sustainability and resource stewardship.</p></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p>Working within this mission, his section contributes to awareness, communication, and community-facing initiatives — aligned with Qatar National Vision 2030&#x27;s pillar of environmental development.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"relative glass-strong rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 overflow-hidden\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -top-24 -right-24 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-maroon-soft blur-3xl\"></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -bottom-32 -left-20 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-gold-faint blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"relative flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center h-9 w-9 rounded-md border border-gold-soft bg-bg-elev/70\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles text-gold\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">Tarsheed · KAHRAMAA</span></div><p class=\"relative mt-6 font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-fg leading-snug text-balance\">Conservation and energy efficiency for Qatar — supported by awareness, communication, and community engagement.</p><div class=\"relative mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-elev/60 p-5 h-full\"><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">Conservation</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-fg-muted leading-relaxed\">Supporting awareness around the responsible use of energy and water.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-elev/60 p-5 h-full\"><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">Efficiency</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-fg-muted leading-relaxed\">Contributing to programs that promote efficient consumption across sectors.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-elev/60 p-5 h-full\"><p class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.26em] uppercase text-gold\">Vision 2030</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm text-fg-muted leading-relaxed\">Aligned with Qatar&#x27;s national pillar of long-term environmental development.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"values\" class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10\"><header class=\"mb-12 md:mb-16 text-center mx-auto max-w-3xl\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5 justify-center\"><span class=\"h-px w-8 bg-gold/70\"></span><span class=\"text-xs tracking-[0.28em] uppercase text-gold font-medium\">Values</span></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance text-fg\">Principles that guide the work.</h2></div></header><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check text-gold transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg\">Integrity</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Acting with honesty, transparency, and ethical responsibility.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flag text-gold transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\"><path d=\"M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z\"></path><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"4\" y1=\"22\" y2=\"15\"></line></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg\">Service to Qatar</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Placing the country and its people at the center of every decision.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-leaf text-gold transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\"><path d=\"M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z\"></path><path d=\"M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg\">Sustainability</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Protecting natural resources for present and future generations.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb text-gold transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-xl md:text-2xl text-fg\">Innovation</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Embracing new ideas, technologies, and approaches to public service.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"group relative h-full bg-bg-elev/80 p-8 md:p-10 transition-colors hover:bg-bg-elev-2/50\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-compass 